[[Image:MK2_grenade_DoD.jpg|thumb]]的开槽弹体。覆盖在其表面的沟槽有助于在投掷时抓牢它，一个常见的误解是手榴弹会沿着这些沟槽形成破片，但事实上并不是这样的。]] 
[[File:Bouncing-mine.svg|left]]释放钢珠的示意图]]

'''破片杀伤'''是指炮兵[[抛射物|抛射物]]（炮弹）、炸弹、[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]等爆炸时，其内部的炸药将外壳撕成许多破片来杀伤目标的过程。

该词在英语中也经常简化为frag，有时对于非预制的破片也称"shards"或"splinters"预制的破片套可以是球形、管形等多种形状，人们还在外壳上刻上花纹，认为这样就会使得破片成为差不多的大小和形状，但事实并非如此<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.technology.org/2018/07/12/why-old-grenades-used-to-have-deep-grooves-why-newer-ones-are-completely-smooth/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-05-19 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426172502/https://www.technology.org/2018/07/12/why-old-grenades-used-to-have-deep-grooves-why-newer-ones-are-completely-smooth/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。人们还经常错误地把"'''shrapnel（榴霰杀伤）'''"当作破片，事实上榴霰弹得名于英军军官施拉普奈的将许多铁珠装进弹头的发明。（这种误解正如把所有肩扛式导弹都叫“[[巴祖卡|巴祖卡]]”一样） <ref>[http://osd.dtic.mil/photos/Nov2003/031111-D-9880W-175.html ''"..shrapnel doctors removed from his knee after the humvee he was riding in hit a land mine.."''] {{Wayback|url=http://osd.dtic.mil/photos/Nov2003/031111-D-9880W-175.html |date=20140201194947 }}, US DOD</ref><ref>[http://csat.au.af.mil/2025/concepts/901159.HTM ''"...An anti-shrapnel netting could reduce the damage done by explosive blasts..."''] {{Wayback|url=http://csat.au.af.mil/2025/concepts/901159.HTM |date=20120520193549 }}, US Air force</ref><ref>[http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/HistoryAndHonour/HeroicDeedsOnOperationsHonoured.htm ''"...The shrapnel had penetrated his chest and lung ..."''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/HistoryAndHonour/HeroicDeedsOnOperationsHonoured.htm |date=20121101073459 }}, UK Ministry of Defence</ref>

